parameters: \nc<Senpai>Congratulations, Saki. There's nothing more I can teach you.

\nc<Senpai>When you first arrived, I wondered what to do... but you're
the first succubus to learn all the techniques I teach in
just one year.

\nc<Senpai>It's true. I've taught you all my techniques. What's left
is... for you, Saki, to live with your feet firmly on the
ground.
\nc<Saki>I always thought my feet were firmly on the ground...

\nc<Senpai>You can even respond naturally to this kind of conversation
now.

\nc<Saki>Hehe. If there's nothing more to learn... does that mean I'm
on the same level as you, Senpai?

\nc<Saki>(Huh? She agreed so easily... Is it true? The talk about
being on the same level as Senpai...)

\nc<Senpai>Then, from the next quarter, we can assign you the same
amount of quotas, right?
